-- This file intentionally has no governance-source snapshot registry gate. The immutable
-- contact ZIP checksums are validated by the generated seed itself. The migrations are applied
-- first, followed byte-for-byte by the generated 26-ward x 12-category contact seed.
-- Routing migration SHA-256: 3a1a35a531494fbeeea876c5b74a541fa9f9bba19a305777f7f461dbe87a002d
-- Email-provenance migration SHA-256: 090e5033c0e0b354bd9b01f47ca8b2045db9ddd0a11c96481daa25f816f9ffa1
-- Seed SHA-256: 8cb4ad1c1307f9d0043a8fcab8d06115f76573ab7bd9c55da4fb2b8399a48a1f
